title.narrative: Orissa Modernising Economy, Govt and Administration

description.narrative: This activity (Orissa Modernising Economy, Govt and Administration) is a component of Orissa Modernising Economy, Govt and Administration reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £13,777,613. This component benefits India, and works in the following sector(s): Public finance management (PFM), Democratic participation and civil society, Industrial policy and administrative management. , with the following implementing partners: Deloitte Touche Tohmatsu India LLP, Ernst & Young, PwC India. The start date is 01-04-2009 and the end date is 31-03-2017.
